==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sketchy
<hw>Sketch"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Containing only an
outline or rough form; being in the manner of a sketch;
incomplete.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The execution is <qex>sketchy</qex> throughout; the head, in
particular, is left in the rough.</q> <rj><qau>J. S.
Harford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skew</ent>⟦br⟧
